&nbsp;
Two patrols arrived and the man, "in evidently altered and uncooperative psychic state", was hit with the taser, "without however that the discharge was effective because of the jacket that the same one wore".
&nbsp;
A colluctation was born and the 37-year-old struck with three back defenders the 35-year-old Deputy Inspector of the State Police with three back defenders. The policeman was transported in red to the Niguarda hospital where it was urgently operated to curb the bleeding caused by the injury of some organs. The attacker is now at the San Vittore prison.

